Stranded In The Wilderness | To Die Alone | Survival Thriller Movie

After suffering a devastating injury while hiking the remote Pacific Crest Trail, Irving must navigate the treacherous wilderness alone, battling not only physical pain but her own inner demons. With the help of a mysterious stranger, she faces her deepest fears to survive.

2025.  Stars: James Tang, Lisa Jacqueline Starrett, James Chrosniak
